 * Setup:
 * - Open the Google Sheet.
 * - Extensions > Apps Script.
 * - Paste this file into Code.gs.
 * - Set CONFIG.serviceMenuPdfFileId to your Drive file ID.
 * - Run installOutreachAutomation() once and approve permissions.
 */

